Announcement of a research-backed playbook to boost GEO/AI brand visibility and how the Spotlight tool can automate the process, plus brief community-orientation and off-topic banter.

highlights.title: Playbook to increase GEO/AI brand visibility with Spotlight automation
highlights.details: Michael shares a research-backed playbook for taking a brand from 0% to 20% visibility in 2 weeks, based on analysis of millions of prompt responses across 1,000+ brands. The session will cover how to implement the strategy with free tools and how their tool Spotlight can automate the workflow. Access/RSVP is via a Google Form.
